#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/admin/admin-page.php:102
msgid "When enabled, uninstalling the plugin removes Deploy & Test settings, audit logs, temporary locks, and cached test summaries from the database."
msgstr "Cand este activ, uninstall-ul pluginului sterge din baza de date setarile Deploy & Test, audit log-urile, lock-urile temporare si sumarul testelor din cache."

