#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:165
msgid "For test actions, each enabled row becomes one button. Use the label for the button text, the workflow file for the GitHub Actions file, and the input name/value pair for the suite or mode you want that button to run."
msgstr "Pentru actiunile de test, fiecare rand activ devine un buton. Foloseste label-ul pentru textul butonului, workflow file pentru fisierul GitHub Actions si perechea input name/value pentru suita sau modul pe care vrei sa il ruleze butonul."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:188
msgid "Each deploy workflow should support manual dispatch. Deploy & Test sends the source ref configured in the Connection tab when it dispatches the workflow."
msgstr "Fiecare workflow de deploy trebuie sa suporte pornire manuala. Deploy & Test trimite source ref-ul configurat in tab-ul Connection atunci cand porneste workflow-ul."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:256
msgid "Use a stable <code>run-name</code> pattern so Deploy & Test can match a run to the expected summary artifact. The recommended pattern is <code>Run ${{ inputs.suite }} tests on ${{ inputs.target_env }}</code>."
msgstr "Foloseste un pattern stabil pentru <code>run-name</code>, ca Deploy & Test sa poata potrivi rularea cu artifactul de summary asteptat. Pattern-ul recomandat este <code>Run ${{ inputs.suite }} tests on ${{ inputs.target_env }}</code>."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:288
msgid "A minimal workflow should run the selected suite, write a compact JSON summary, and upload that summary even when tests fail."
msgstr "Un workflow minimal ar trebui sa ruleze suita selectata, sa scrie un summary JSON compact si sa incarce acel summary chiar si cand testele esueaza."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:328
msgid "The recommended file path inside the artifact is:"
msgstr "Calea recomandata pentru fisierul din artifact este:"

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:334
msgid "Deploy & Test looks for a file named deploy-update-summary.json inside the artifact archive, so the parent folder can be different if your test framework needs another layout."
msgstr "Deploy & Test cauta un fisier numit deploy-update-summary.json in arhiva artifactului, deci folderul parinte poate fi diferit daca framework-ul de test are nevoie de alta structura."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:399
msgid "If Delete plugin data on uninstall is enabled, uninstalling the plugin also removes the stored settings, audit log, temporary locks, and cached test summaries."
msgstr "Daca Delete plugin data on uninstall este activ, uninstall-ul pluginului sterge si setarile salvate, audit log-ul, lock-urile temporare si summary-urile de test din cache."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/admin/general-tab.php:581
msgid "The requested test run was not found in the configured testing repository."
msgstr ""
"Rularea de test solicitata nu a fost gasita in repository-ul de testare "
"configurat."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/admin/general-tab.php:585
msgid "The requested test run does not belong to one of the configured test workflows."
msgstr ""
"Rularea de test solicitata nu apartine unuia dintre workflow-urile de test "
"configurate."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/admin/general-tab.php:736
msgid "The test summary artifact contains too many files to load in WordPress. Open the GitHub run to view the full report."
msgstr ""
"Artifactul cu sumarul de test contine prea multe fisiere pentru a fi "
"incarcat in WordPress. Deschide rularea GitHub pentru raportul complet."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/admin/general-tab.php:749
#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/admin/general-tab.php:758
msgid "The deploy-update-summary.json file is too large to load in WordPress. Open the GitHub run to view the full report."
msgstr ""
"Fisierul deploy-update-summary.json este prea mare pentru a fi incarcat in "
"WordPress. Deschide rularea GitHub pentru raportul complet."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/github.php:255
#, php-format
msgid "The GitHub artifact archive is too large to load in WordPress. Limit: %s. Open the GitHub run to view the full report."
msgstr ""
"Arhiva artifactului GitHub este prea mare pentru a fi incarcata in "
"WordPress. Limita: %s. Deschide rularea GitHub pentru raportul complet."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/how-to-use-page/how-to-use-page.php:35
msgid "WordPress Editors can trigger the configured deploy and test actions, but only Administrators can change plugin configuration, workflow settings, cleanup settings, or audit-log access. This is intended for teams that want trusted non-technical WordPress users to run approved workflows without granting administrator or GitHub access."
msgstr ""
"Editorii WordPress pot declansa actiunile de deploy si test configurate, dar "
"doar Administratorii pot modifica configuratia pluginului, setarile "
"workflow-urilor, setarile de cleanup sau accesul la audit log. Aceasta "
"impartire este intentionata pentru echipe care vor ca utilizatori WordPress "
"non-tehnici si de incredere sa ruleze workflow-uri aprobate fara acces de "
"administrator sau acces GitHub."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/settings.php:197
msgid "GitHub owner must contain only letters, numbers, and single hyphens, and cannot start or end with a hyphen."
msgstr ""
"Owner-ul GitHub trebuie sa contina doar litere, numere si cratime simple si "
"nu poate incepe sau termina cu o cratima."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/settings.php:202
msgid "Repository names must contain only letters, numbers, dots, underscores, and hyphens."
msgstr ""
"Numele repository-urilor trebuie sa contina doar litere, numere, puncte, "
"underscore-uri si cratime."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/settings.php:208
msgid "Source refs cannot contain spaces, control characters, or Git ref special characters."
msgstr ""
"Ref-urile sursa nu pot contine spatii, caractere de control sau caractere "
"speciale pentru Git ref."

#: wordpress-deploy-and-test-plugin/deploy-and-test/includes/settings.php:214
msgid "Workflow files must be YAML filenames such as deploy-preview.yml or tests.yaml."
msgstr ""
"Fisierele workflow trebuie sa fie fisiere YAML, de exemplu deploy-preview.yml "
"sau tests.yaml."

